    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267070/extras/efee494bede940b3726b36d10c08cc16.avif?t=1761545642\" width=600 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >早上好，欢迎乘坐连接M市和L市的单轨交通系统。这项了不起的工程杰作每天让成千上万的人在两座城市之间往返，相互交流。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天，在悬挂于海湾上方的轨道上，在行驶的车厢里，都会诞生出一百个新的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天，平凡的人身上发生着不平凡的事。这就是他们的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267070/extras/1940d8d03b87de9d9b64f82f72acbefe.avif?t=1761545642\" width=600 height=84 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267070/extras/072fb5204abeb031c5c6321237d7b05c.poster.avif?t=1761545642\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267070/extras/072fb5204abeb031c5c6321237d7b05c.webm?t=1761545642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267070/extras/072fb5204abeb031c5c6321237d7b05c.mp4?t=1761545642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>西尔维和阿马尔，分别来自M市和L市。两个互不相识的人，却通过他们每天共享的单轨列车影响着彼此的生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们每天在不同的时间往返于两座城市之间。每天，他们都会选择在单轨列车上与谁交谈，如何对待他们的同行者，以及当单轨列车驶过海湾时该做些什么。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一天都是他们共同故事的一个新章节，你可以自己写，或者和朋友通过异步多人模式共同书写这个故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267070/extras/76c9468dacbc7cad85b33bb8a6add195.avif?t=1761545642\" width=600 height=84 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267070/extras/c4a64467c4c89533305b195105c29fa4.poster.avif?t=1761545642\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267070/extras/c4a64467c4c89533305b195105c29fa4.webm?t=1761545642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267070/extras/c4a64467c4c89533305b195105c29fa4.mp4?t=1761545642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>当你每天控制西尔维和阿马尔时，你会在通勤途中遇到数十个人。如何与他们互动均取决于你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在单轨列车上做出的选择会影响他们的故事，或者说，你和他们共同创造和参与的故事，每一个决定和每一次互动都会让故事走向不同的结局，西尔维和阿马尔也会有不同的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267070/extras/075b3f03e3530d7075699205572af55c.avif?t=1761545642\" width=600 height=84 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267070/extras/22684e164c003266dabce58fdf7704e3.poster.avif?t=1761545642\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267070/extras/22684e164c003266dabce58fdf7704e3.webm?t=1761545642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267070/extras/22684e164c003266dabce58fdf7704e3.mp4?t=1761545642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>随着单轨故事的展开，这两座由轨道连接的城市的故事也随之展开。这两座城市面临着动荡和不确定，就像每天乘坐单轨列车穿梭于它们之间的人们一样。他们的命运很可能不是由人们做什么决定的，而是由他们如何对待彼此决定的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者说，是由你决定他们如何对待彼此的。在单人模式下控制西尔维和阿马尔，或者找一个朋友，通过异步多人模式体验这个非线性的故事。在等待单轨列车的时候，探索每座城市的单轨车站，每个车站都有自己的互动和秘密。</p>",
